{"tid":836756,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：普巴唔再係副隊長","createTime":"2018-09-26T01:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T01:47:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17bb8f51ece9d2d5e81d9075049b8fba66e7a1c0","tid":836756,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/8/298/22991993298/23006913253_600x341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F8%2F298%2F22991993298%2F23006913253_600x341.jpg&h=73a2f568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=K%2BiddrwNjGpv%2BTt7PTNmeWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=2bbf148f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯領隊摩連奴證實，法國中場保羅普巴不會再出任球隊副隊長。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯於周二在英聯盃爆冷被打比郡踢出局，早於賽前，有傳領隊摩連奴與法國球星保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）不和，並已告知普巴不會再出任球隊隊長，被問到此事時，摩佬作出回應：「（就報道）唯一事實是我決定普巴不再是球隊的副隊長。不過沒有爭執，沒有問題。」<br />\n<br />\n「那個決定保羅不再是第2隊長的人，是之前決定讓他出任第2隊長的人──是我。我是可以作出決定的領隊，沒爭執，沒問題，只是這決定我不必去解釋。」上周六英超，曼聯主場被升班馬狼隊逼和1:1，賽後摩連奴批評球員的作戰態度，而普巴就作出反擊，指球隊在主場出戰該進攻，有批評摩佬戰術之嫌，他事後指說話被曲解。<br />\n<br />\n被問到輸波關鍵時，摩連奴說：「當我們可以入球時卻做不到，在半場的時候，我說出去仗一樣的話，那就是沒有致命一擊。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"a4335431b43aebe795f2dae98574770b1670a842","tid":836756,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/T2AmoAqrjAluU/200.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FT2AmoAqrjAluU%2F200.gif&h=3fc528d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3de133e6fae188c58aeb4782271df5e6f1ccc83","tid":836756,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:29:28.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"70b171f7e379660cbb0ad014186554549b4c54a9","tid":836756,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:38:19.000Z","msg":"鬼"},{"pid":"260dff5e569cf088aca6068638ca11211ec615ba","tid":836756,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}